{
  "texts": [
    "There are several recommendations that could help out with these problems and that might help foster an AI-driven culture in the classrooms:",
    "Workshops: The school could provide workshops specifically tailored to help teachers understand what is going on in the world of AI and what tools there are to aid them in creating an AI-inclusive classroom environment. 2.",
    "Regular Updates: There could be outlets (i.e.",
    "in the form of newsletters, lunch-meetings, online-events, etc.)",
    "that aim towards keeping staff and lecturers up-to-date so that people are aware of the newest tools, apps, and approaches that could be useful for their lectures. 3."
  ]
}